{"word":"H5957 - עָלַם - ʻâlam - aw-lam' - For ever","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עָלַם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʻâlam"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>aw-lam'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>For ever"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"பூர்வம், என்றும், என்றென்றைக்கும், நித்தியம் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"perpetuity, antiquity, forever"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Noun Masculine / பெயர்ச்சொல் (ஆண்பால்)</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> (Chaldee); corresponding to <a href=\"#/H5769 - עֹולָם - ʻôwlâm - o-lawm'/5769\">H5769</a>; <i>remote</i> time, that is, the <i>future</i> or <i>past</i> indefinitely; often adverbially <i>forever: - </i>for([n-]) ever (lasting), old."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4606 - מֵעָל - mêʻâl - may-awl'/4606\">H4606</a>, <a href=\"#/H5954 - עֲלַל - ʻălal - al-al'/5954\">H5954</a>, <a href=\"#/H5957 - עָלַם - ʻâlam - aw-lam'/5957\">H5957</a>, <a href=\"#/H5962 - עַלְמִי - ʻAlmîy - al-mee'/5962\">H5962</a>, <a href=\"#/H5967 - עֲלַע - ʻălaʻ - al-ah'/5967\">H5967</a>, <a href=\"#/H5972 - עַם - ʻam - am/5972\">H5972</a>"}]}